msgid "Hiro's room."
msgstr "廣人的房間。"

msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

msgid "I'd rather not go in without permission..."
msgstr "我不想未經許可就進去..."

msgid "You shouldn't go in."
msgstr "妳不應該進去。"

msgid "You won't go in."
msgstr "妳不會進去的。"

msgid "Some books and magazines."
msgstr "一些書籍和雜誌。"

msgid "No reading space would be complete without decorative books."
msgstr "如果沒裝飾用書的話，就稱不上是閱讀空間了。"

msgid "It's a decoration of some sorts. You don't really know."
msgstr "這是某種裝飾品。妳真的不太清楚。"

msgid "It's a painting, similar to the one downstairs."
msgstr "一幅畫，和樓下的很相似。"

msgid "A painting."
msgstr "一幅畫。"

msgid "It's a painting, identical to the one on the left."
msgstr "一幅畫，與左邊的一模一樣。"

msgid "It's a painting, identical to the one on the right."
msgstr "一幅畫，與右邊的一模一樣。"

msgid "Winter vacation photos. You're not in any of them."
msgstr "冬天假期的照片。妳不在任何一張之中。"

msgid "A pretty plant. The buds are non-edible."
msgstr "漂亮的植物。花蕾不可食用。"

msgid "A plant."
msgstr "植物。"

msgid "Some old family pictures."
msgstr "一些老舊的家庭照片。"

msgid "The backyard can be seen from here."
msgstr "可以從這裡看到後院。"

msgid "Something is written on the door:"
msgstr "有東西寫在門上："

msgid "\"What is this room? You spent a lot of time in there."
msgstr "\"這是什麼房間？妳在這裡花了很多時間。"

msgid "Always finding new places to hide away from the world."
msgstr "總是找到新的地方來逃避世界。"

msgid "Did you ever stop hiding?\""
msgstr "妳停止逃避過嗎？\""
